  "Description": {
    "English": "A generalised upgrade for all Multi-Tool <span class=\"name name-technology\">weapon systems</span>, causing its projectiles to resonate dramatically upon impact with any appropriate electromagnetic field.<br><br>Will significantly increase the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">damage</span> dealt to any organic and inorganic entities that are currently <span class=\"name name-stellar\">stunned</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "适用于所有多用途工具<span class=\"name name-technology\">武器系统</span>的通用型升级组件，能够使投射物与接触到的任何电磁场产生剧烈共鸣。<br><br>这种组件能够大幅提高对处于<span class=\"name name-stellar\">晕眩</span>状态的有机与无机体造成的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">伤害</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "工具組<span class=\"name name-technology\">武器系統</span>的通用升級，讓射彈在與任何適當的電磁力場碰撞時，產生劇烈的共振。<br><br>針對所有處於<span class=\"name name-stellar\">暈眩</span>狀態的有機和無機存在體，顯著提高其受到的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">傷害</span>。"
  },
